          <h3>Waitlist Management</h3>
          <p><span aria-hidden="true">üìã</span> Automated Processing</p>
        </header>
        <div>
          <p>Automated waitlist processing with email notifications and seamless enrollment when spots become available.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article data-component="card" role="listitem">
        <header>
          <h3>Staff Management</h3>
          <p><span aria-hidden="true">üë•</span> Role-Based Access</p>
